{
  "chapter": 33,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十三回\"宝剑无罪\"讲述了楚留香、胡铁花等人被困神水宫菩提庵，与神秘的青衣尼（大师姐）对峙。胡铁花想出敲击石壁铁环的计策，引诱大师姐打开密门。进入佛堂后，发现李红袖和宋甜儿昏迷不醒，还有蒙面的一男一女。青衣尼突然出手攻击，胡铁花被窗外暗算者偷袭，幸得蒙面女子（曲无容）用蒲团相救。南苹为楚留香等人求情，胡铁花这才发现救命恩人是曲无容。此时窗外传来神秘组织的威胁，要求交出叛徒。受伤的蒙面客（一点红）冲出去，被楚留香拦住。楚留香认出一点红，揭露了神秘组织的铜牌标志，劝说一点红联手对抗这个邪恶组织。一点红透露自己是被该组织养大，武功也是他们传授，陷入忠义两难的困境。本章通过\"宝剑无罪\"的隐喻，揭示了武器本身无善恶，关键在于握剑之手的主题。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南苹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实各位也用不着太担心，大师姐本是我们本门姐妹中武功最高的一人，她如今虽已残废，武功并未失去，一定能将那些人击退的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她若有把握能将那些人击退，一定也早就动手了，又怎会等到现在呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南苹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是……可是我师父常说，大师姐的武功已绝不在当今武林最负盛名的十大高手之下，那些人的武功难道还能比她更高么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "敢和楚留香作对的人，自然一定有两下子。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_du_xing",
      "speaker_name": "戴独行",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "香帅能想得出那些人是谁么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我纵能猜得出那些人是谁，于事又有何补?",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我现在只希望你们的大师姐已看出自己的武功绝非对方的敌手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南苹",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只因她若被逼得无法可施时，也许就会不顾一切，将这道门打开了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_du_xing",
      "speaker_name": "戴独行",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，这就叫置之死地而后生。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南苹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若是换了别人，到了绝境时，也许会这么做的，但我大师姐宁死也不会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_du_xing",
      "speaker_name": "戴独行",
      "listener": "char_nan_ping",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南苹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我大师姐就因为无心泄露了本宫的出入道路，所以才受到重责，她这次又怎敢再重蹈覆辙?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南苹",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你这是干什么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就叫置之死地而后生。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_du_xing",
      "speaker_name": "戴独行",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，那些人听到地下有声音传出，就必定已能猜到神水宫的入口是在什么地方了，他们若已知道神水宫的入口在何处，那位大师姐也就没有什么隐瞒可言了，她若已没有顾忌，也许就会将这道门打开。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是个笨人，只能想得出这种笨法子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到了聪明人都无法可施之时，笨人想出来的法子一定最有用。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "老臭虫，看来我又欠你一次情。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这次救你命的倒不是我。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "是谁?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "text": "姑娘救了我的命，我却去谢别人，实在不好意思得很，但姑娘也莫要见怪，我这人虽笨，倒也知道好歹，以后姑娘无论要我做什么，要我水里去我就水里去，要我火里去我就火里去。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南苹",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我大师姐想要问问你们的来历，和本宫可有什么渊源……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南苹",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我知道你们和本宫有很深的渊源，否则师父她老人家就不会叫你们来这里了，所以你们还是向大师姐说明的好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_ping",
      "text": "此中详情，一时间也不能详说，等姑娘见到令师时，自然会明白的，此刻还是先应付这里的事要紧。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，我只想知道鬼鬼祟祟躲在外面暗算人的那些小子究竟是谁?我好歹也要给他们个教训。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_ni",
      "text": "你……大师真的不能说话?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_ni",
      "text": "但大师却能听得到我们说话?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_ni",
      "text": "你明明听得见，为何偏偏要说听不见呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南苹",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我大师姐真的听不见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_nan_ping",
      "text": "若是听不见，她怎会点头摇头?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "求求你们快说出来吧，莫要再打哑谜了，我简直已快被急得发疯。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "窗外一人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此事和各位全无关系，方才那一剑也只不过是聊以示警而已，毫无伤人之意，只要各位将本门的叛徒交出来，我们立刻就走，秋毫无犯；但各位若是定要来淌这浑水，只怕就难免要玉石俱焚了。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们究竟是什么人?谁是你们的叛徒?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "我们既已到了这里，一切事就该听凭大师作主，你此刻若是冲了出去，岂非辜负了她老人家的一番好意?",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "窗外那人",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "大丈夫做事敢做敢当，堂堂男子汉却逃到这里来求妇人女子的庇护，算得了什么英雄好汉?简直连我们的人都被你丢光了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "此事与你无关，闪开!",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "你的事就是我的事，怎会和我无关呢?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你……你是谁?我不认得你。",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "就算你不认得我，我还是认得你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "红兄，我知道你心高气傲，素来不肯求人，但到了现在你若还要隐瞒，就未免将我看得不够朋友了吧?",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "红兄，曲姑娘……唉!我真该死，竟没有认出是你们。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我不能好好照顾他，反而要来求……求人，我实在觉得无颜再见你们之面了，可是……可是……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "这也是我该死，红兄若非被我这瞎了眼的混蛋误伤成残废，现在又怎会受人欺负!何况，曲姑娘你今天又救了我一命，我……我……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁要来找一点红的麻烦，就先来找我胡铁花吧!",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_du_xing",
      "speaker_name": "戴独行",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好猴儿崽子，真下毒手呀!",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_lu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "黄鲁直",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些人剑法辛辣狠毒，自成一家，你们小心了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这是我的事，你们何必插手?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "小胡对你是自觉于心有愧，你若不让他出去打上一架，他只怕真的要急疯了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但这件事却是无论谁也管不了的。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你也用不着多问，你若真是我的朋友，就带着他们快走。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "以你我的交情，你还有什么事不能对我说的吗?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "快走!快走!你若再不走，莫怪我跟你翻脸。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他实在有难言的苦衷……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "text": "你看见外面那棵树了吗?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "看见了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "text": "一棵树从地上长出来，也和人一样，是为了要成长、结实、传宗接代，但现在它却被这些人的剑光砍得乱七八糟，这是不是很可惜?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "text": "无论是人的生命也好，树的生命也好，它若还未成长就被摧毁了，总是件可恨的事，但你能说这是剑的错吗?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这……这我也不知道。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "text": "剑本身并没有错，错的只是那只握剑的手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你……你已知道他的事了?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这是哪里来的?",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这只手，只怕就是世上最神秘、最邪恶、也最有权力的一只手了，因为他不但在暗中掌握着无数人的生死，而且还令人死得糊里糊涂，不明不白，直到死后还不知世上有这只手存在。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "世上只要有一只这样的手存在，至少就有一两人难免生于恐惧，而死于黑暗，若将这只手消灭了，大家的日子都会过得太平得多，是吗?",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你想消灭他?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "你纵然不想消灭他，他也要消灭你的。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "我知道他一定是很可怕的人，但无论多可怕的人我都见过了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我知道你对任何人都无所畏惧，可是他……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "到了现在，你难道还不愿助我一臂之力?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你莫忘了，我是他养大的，我的武功也是他传授的，他纵然要杀我，我也不能出卖他。",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "这是你的义气，我绝不勉强你……我只问你，他今天来了没有?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他今日若来了，外面只怕早已住手了!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "因为当今世上，他的剑法已无人能比。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    }
  ],
